@startuml seq-auth
skinparam shadowing false
actor Usuario
participant "App\n(cliente)" as App
participant "API\n(AuthController/Service)" as API
database "BD" as DB

== Inicio de sesión ==
Usuario -> App : introduce credenciais
App -> API : POST /auth/login (email, contrasinal)
API -> DB : verifica usuario e hash BCrypt
API -> API : xera access token (JWT, RSA)\ne refresh token
API -> DB : garda refresh token
API --> App : { accessToken, refreshToken }

== Petición autenticada con token caducado ==
App -> API : GET /recurso (Bearer access token)
API --> App : 401 Unauthorized
App -> API : POST /auth/refresh (refreshToken)
API -> DB : valida refresh token
API --> App : novo accessToken
App -> API : reintenta GET /recurso (novo Bearer)
API --> App : 200 OK
@enduml
